dct_title_s: Corsica 1;50,000 / drawn and reproduced at the Ordnance Survey ; U. S. Army Map Service
dct_description_sm: "Contour interval 20 metres. Contours have been interpolated from spot heights and hachures on the French 1:80,000." Geographical coverage completed in 16 sheets. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Includes index to sheets, compilation data, incidence of grid letters, reliability diagrams. Shows five classes of roads and tracks, and various types of vegetation. Includes: Corsican topographical terms & abbreviations.
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section, 1943.
